title: AHS10: Premiere Date REVEALED
author: American Horror Story 10
comment:
Are you serious??
I literally thought it would be no later then September or this year. 🤦🏼‍♀️

It's a little sad we have to wait, but it's not really surprising. I kind of expected a release date for next year due to COVID. While it does seem like a while away, I don't mind waiting if it means the cast and production for season 10 stay safe.

I'm so hyped that they gave us airing date but it seems like an eternity away from now......ugh..I cannot wait...but I really thought it was going to be sept/oct 2021 at least...they're clearly still filming...its going to be worth the wait I'm sure cause we know Ryan Murphy is a pure genius!!!!!!!
